{"tid":247163,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【全貴居屋】冠熹苑2房實呎逼1.6萬膺全港居屋王","createTime":"2017-05-17T14:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T14:45:24.000Z","uid":35408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e9d1282b5504143105d56cb3773fdba188b110f7","tid":247163,"uid":35408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:45:24.000Z","msg":"【全貴居屋】冠熹苑2房實呎逼1.6萬膺全港居屋王<br />\n<br />\n市區居屋再創新高價，市場消息指，何文田冠熹苑中層09室，實用423方呎(建築569方呎)，兩房間隔，剛以約672萬元(已補地價)售出，實呎15887元(建呎11810元)，除成交價創屋苑新高外，呎價更貴絶全港已補地價居屋。原業主於2000年5月以112.1萬元(未補地價)一手購入，料獲利甚豐。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170517/s00003/1495021204080\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170517%2Fs00003%2F1495021204080&d=oZ19EkYl1LXsHPE32KnJvROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=b3c3a3c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170517%2Fs00003%2F1495021204080&h=c5d05e6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170517/s00003/1495021204080</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nfat fat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}